World Diamond Demand May Expand 8% This Year on Recovery, Even-Zohar Says

-- B y   J e r r y   B u n g u
-- 
2011-04-04T15:08:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/world-diamond-demand-may-expand-8-this-year-on-recovery-even-zohar-says.html
World diamond demand will probably
increase 8 percent this year as the global economy recovers,
said Chaim Even-Zohar, principal at industry consulting company
Tacy Ltd.  Demand for the gems grew by 6.5 percent last year, Even-
Zohar said in a presentation today at a conference in Gaborone,
